C2v25sOhvw">Tả hoài kỳ 2 - 寫懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/T%E1%BA%B7c-tho%C3%A1i-th%E1%BB%8B-quan-l%E1%BA%A1i/poem-MPkFriAnpoLgV8ElT4nkgg">Tặc thoái thị quan lại - 賊退示官吏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/author-9Y30zD24BFXrRqipoBvcFA">Nguyên Kết</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Tr%E1%BB%ABng-Chi/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o/poem-dwsKivXoJ5TA_Qil5ceCng">Tòng quân khẩu hào - 從軍口號</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Tr%E1%BB%ABng-Chi/author-V8R7nhhotOVWLkm8vPg4Jg">Tiền Trừng Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
